<lb n="0481a25"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu type="經" level="1" n="2" label="佛說咒賊經"/><head>佛說&CB00057;賊經</head>
<lb n="0481a26"/><p>南無佛　南無法　南無比丘僧　南無諸過
<lb n="0481a27"/>去七佛　南無諸佛弟子。南無利閉利鬼神
<lb n="0481a28"/>王禮是已說此&CB00057;經即從如願。</p>
<lb n="0481a29"/><p>北方有山名揵陀摩訶衍。有鬼神名利閉利。
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0987.0481b" n="0481b"/>
<lb n="0481b01"/>居<note n="0481010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">山＝止【元】【明】</note><app n="0481010"><lem>山</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">止</rdg></app>彼有是四<note n="0481011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">師＝&CB00106;【元】【明】</note><app n="0481011"><lem>師</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00106;</rdg></app>弟子　安陀尼　閉摩尼
<lb n="0481b02"/>　攢呵尼　令賊忘閉尼　令賊急坐　抄多
<lb n="0481b03"/>摩尼　令賊急生　立攢呵尼　令賊愚癡
<lb n="0481b04"/>　如是<note n="0481012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">烏＝鳥【三】</note><note n="0481012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">烏＝鳥【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0481012"><lem>烏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">鳥</rdg></app>不羅利陀提摩　閉迦利當搭賊口
<lb n="0481b05"/><note n="0481013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">齒＋（噤）【三】</note><note n="0481013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">齒＋（噤）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0481013"><lem>齒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">齒噤</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0481b06"/><p>至解縷乃解我某甲擁護。辟除凶惡害賊者。
<lb n="0481b07"/>皆銷滅令其<note n="0481014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（安）＋隱【三】</note><note n="0481014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（安）＋隱【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0481014"><lem>隱</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">安隱</rdg></app>。初說是&CB00057;賊經時。當以二十
<lb n="0481b08"/>九日為呵利提耶。然燈燒膠香為伊怖然。七
<lb n="0481b09"/>燈脫散華。為鬼子母然七燈。鬼子母前讀是
<lb n="0481b10"/>七遍。乃吉。合號利離鬼子王得福德。為然七
<lb n="0481b11"/>燈<note n="0481015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乃＝及【三】</note><note n="0481015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乃＝及【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0481015"><lem>乃</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">及</rdg></app>燒香散華。</p></div1>
